  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large bamboo steamer over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes, artichoke hearts, paella seasoning, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the rice and chicken broth to the steamer. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover the steamer with a lid.",
    "Cook for 10-12 minutes, or until the rice is tender and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and lemon juice. Serve hot.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
  ],
